language Essence 1.3

given v, b, r, k, lambda : int(1..)

find incidence : matrix indexed by [int(1..v), int(1..b)] of int(0..1)

such that
    forAll point : int(1..v) .
        (sum block : int(1..b) . incidence[point, block]) = r,
    forAll block : int(1..b) .
        (sum point : int(1..v) . incidence[point, block]) = k,
    forAll p1 : int(1..v) . forAll p2 : int(p1+1..v) .
        (sum block : int(1..b) . incidence[p1, block] * incidence[p2, block]) = lambda
